<i>Just imagine it's the sea.</i>

166
00:10:43,167 --> 00:10:46,733
<i>Pretend this is the ocean.</i>

167
00:10:46,733 --> 00:10:49,267
<i>Think of this as chicken and beer by the shore.</i>

168
00:10:49,267 --> 00:10:51,633
<i>But, this isn't the sea.</i>

169
00:10:51,633 --> 00:10:54,133
<i>That's why we're imagining.</i>

170
00:10:54,133 --> 00:10:55,567
<i>We can't go there,</i>

171
00:10:55,567 --> 00:10:58,433
<i>but imagine us eating chicken after work.</i>

172
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:07,900
<i>With waves and seagulls...</i>

173
00:11:13,133 --> 00:11:15,033
<i>Si Wan.</i>

174
00:11:15,033 --> 00:11:18,700
<i>Do you think we'll ever
really eat chicken and beer</i>

175
00:11:18,700 --> 00:11:20,000
<i>by the sea someday?</i>

176
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,800
<i>Of course, we will.</i>

177
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:23,700
<i>It's not that hard.</i>

178
