<i>I haven't heard anything like that.</i>

188
00:12:10,233 --> 00:12:13,800
They just asked me to take good care
of the dog and bring it back.

189
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:15,767
Understood.

190
00:12:16,567 --> 00:12:18,200
Yes.

191
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,904
Ah, Mr. O.

192
00:12:19,904 --> 00:12:23,700
Could you at least leave me their contact?

193
00:12:23,700 --> 00:12:24,700
<i>Okay, fine.</i>

194
00:12:24,700 --> 00:12:27,467
<i>But keep it secret.</i>

195
00:12:27,467 --> 00:12:29,867
Yes, don't worry.

196
00:12:29,867 --> 00:12:31,067
<i>I'll hang up now.</i>

197
00:12:31,067 --> 00:12:32,667
Okay.

198
00:12:40,800 --> 00:12:44,333
<i>Only contact this number for emergencies.</i>

199
