[One Family Animal Hospital]

200
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:21,267
I'm sorry.

201
00:13:21,267 --> 00:13:23,833
Had a tough time, huh?

202
00:13:23,833 --> 00:13:25,600
Let's go now.

203
00:13:27,400 --> 00:13:29,167
Ms. Kang Yeo Reum.

204
