235
00:15:13,433 --> 00:15:15,467
Right now, Ms. Kang Yeo Reum,

236
00:15:15,467 --> 00:15:18,400
you have no information about Genie,

237
00:15:18,400 --> 00:15:20,900
which could be extremely dangerous for him.

238
00:15:20,900 --> 00:15:25,000
There's a lump around Genie's chest right now.

239
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,633
What?

240
00:15:26,633 --> 00:15:30,300
This could be nothing,

241
00:15:30,300 --> 00:15:32,933
or it could be something serious.

242
00:15:33,800 --> 00:15:35,633
Contact the owner immediately

243
00:15:35,633 --> 00:15:38,200
and get a biopsy done first.

244
00:15:50,033 --> 00:15:52,167
<i>This trip is specifically</i>

245
00:15:52,167 --> 00:15:55,433
<i>tied to a confidentiality agreement.</i>

246
00:15:55,433 --> 00:15:57,567
Confidentiality maintenance...

247
00:15:57,567 --> 00:15:58,600
Confidentiality maintenance.

248
00:15:58,600 --> 00:16:03,267
<i>Anyway, you're responsible
for Genie during this trip.</i>

249
00:16:04,067 --> 00:16:06,933
Right, I'm his guardian now.

250
00:16:14,333 --> 00:16:16,367
<i>- The subscriber you dialed...</i>
- Huh?

251
00:16:18,400 --> 00:16:20,000
What?

252
00:16:22,967 --> 00:16:26,700
<i>The subscriber you dialed is unavailable,
connecting to voicemail...</i>

253
00:16:26,700 --> 00:16:28,600
What's wrong with this guy?

254
00:16:33,033 --> 00:16:36,033
<i>The subscriber you dialed is unavailable,
connecting to voicemail.</i>

255
00:16:36,033 --> 00:16:39,000
<i>After the beep, the call charges will apply.</i>

256
00:16:41,167 --> 00:16:43,433
<i>Hello, this is Kang Yeo Reum.</i>

257
00:16:43,433 --> 00:16:46,367
<i>I'm calling about Genie's health issue.</i>

258
00:16:46,367 --> 00:16:50,133
<i>The hospital requested a biopsy.</i>

259
00:16:50,133 --> 00:16:52,633
<i>Were you aware of this?</i>

260
00:16:53,300 --> 00:16:55,633
<i>Just focus on your trip and do it right.</i>

261
00:16:55,633 --> 00:16:57,267
Unbelievable.

262
00:16:57,967 --> 00:16:59,800
What kind of person is this?

263
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:05,900
You want me to hang it here?

264
00:17:07,300 --> 00:17:08,733
Can you try moving it a bit higher?

